Title: Gash to dash for a good cause
Content: Lawyer-turned-ultra-marathoner Samantha Gash is ready to kick off her 3,800-km dash across the breadth of the country on August 22 to raise funds for improved access to education among underprivileged
Author: Samarth Soni
